NEW JERSEY DIVISION OF CHILD PROTECTION AND PERMANENCY, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
T.S., Defendant-Petitioner,
and
M.B. and E.P., Defendants. In the Matter of N.S. and T.B., Minors-Respondents. C-201 Sept. Term 2017
079245 Supreme Court of New Jersey. October 20, 2017

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004936-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
